review_title: so so for now may with work
one_reviews_text: so far I have swam ashore many many many timesl, only to get my pack and be killed. Am really sick of hearing the same call over and over  and iver and over again should be able to skip the crap. Once the pack is found and you get a gun takes several head shots witha rife and they keep coming. they can shoot over thier shoulder and run faster than a man with nothing but a knife and usless guns
review_feedback: You there, thanks for playing Another Dawn! You need to swim towards the beach, collect your backpack and then move to the cavern on the other side in order to proceed to level 2. KR Games team

review_title: not good with oculus rift touch
one_reviews_text: not good with oculus rift touch pad, the shooting is off have to use the 14 clip to kill one man and ammuntion is very scarce.
review_feedback:
Hi there, thanks for playing Another Dawn! In order to proceed in the game, you need to collect your backpack first, then move to the cavern on the other side of the jungle.
